title: NDFD, NOAA, Significant Wave Height in GOM coastal waters, USA, July 21, 2010
name: NDFD, NOAA, Significant Wave Height in GOM coastal waters, USA, July 21, 2010
description:
The poly shapefile shows significant wave height data for portions of coastal waters in the GOM.

The data was extracted from NDFD's extraction program and then converted to shapefile. The NDFD wave height predictions are valid between 11 Hrs UTC to 18 Hrs UTC on 22nd.

Look elsewhere on Finder! for wave data over the next several days. Use key word "Wave height".


http://www.nws.noaa.gov/ndfd/technical.htm
